com.smartnsoft.droid4me.analytics

Annotation Type AnalyticsLogger.AnalyticsEnabledLoggerAnnotation


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Target(value=TYPE)
public static @interface AnalyticsLogger.AnalyticsEnabledLoggerAnnotation
    An annotation which enables to express that an entity, usually an Activity or a Fragment, wishes to report analytics usage.

    Use this annotation, when you explicitly want the underlying entity to report an activity.

    See Also:
    AnalyticsLogger.AnalyticsDisabledLoggerAnnotation
